structured.description: An interface for amenity services that allows for the creation, retrieval, deletion, and updating of amenities within a community. The interface includes four methods: createAmenities, getAmenityDetails, deleteAmenity, and listAllAmenities. These methods allow for the manipulation of amenities in a community, including adding, retrieving, deleting, and updating amenities.

items.description: provides methods for creating, retrieving, deleting, and listing amenities in a community.
items.name: AmenityService
